Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.48,0:28:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all up to you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.04,0:28:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.91,0:28:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How many servings, sweetie?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.43,0:28:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to have a serving.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.85,0:28:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,One serving, huh? Gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.58,0:28:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why only one serving?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.10,0:28:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like one bowl of rice noodle soup.\N Other customers can come here to support the owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.35,0:28:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The owner may get more support from other people, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.21,0:28:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, one serving for this little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.84,0:28:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Which grade are you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.44,0:28:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in the first grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.33,0:28:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the same age as Tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.35,0:28:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.48,0:28:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why so much, girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.06,0:28:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You paid VND100,000 for this bowl, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.51,0:28:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a ton.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.40,0:28:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Thanh.\N VND300,000 for the first serving.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.71,0:28:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.73,0:28:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like 2 servings, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.64,0:28:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 2 servings, huh?\N- Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.26,0:28:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.54,0:28:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,VND60,000 for 2 servings.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.35,0:28:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Two servings, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.63,0:28:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are your servings.\N Thanks a lot for supporting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.64,0:28:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.42,0:28:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,May I have 10 servings?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.92,0:29:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten servings.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.00,0:29:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, whoa! 10 servings!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.48,0:29:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sis.\N We've prepared just 150 servings today.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.66,0:29:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of people are still waiting to support Thanh.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.64,0:29:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you mind buying fewer servings?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.64,0:29:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.26,0:29:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- How many servings would you like to buy?\N- Just 5, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.39,0:29:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I appreciate it much.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.07,0:29:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure that you give her 5 servings.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.78,0:29:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Five servings for you.\N We're preparing a bag of broth. Just give us a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.49,0:29:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How much in total?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.71,0:29:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The owner sells it at VND20,000/bowl\N but today you can give him as much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.45,0:29:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- VND100,000, right?\N- That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.41,0:29:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she's given me VND400,000.\N Thanks a bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.09,0:29:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thanks, sis. \N- May I take a photo with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.79,0:29:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- I have 2 servings, please.\N- Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.27,0:29:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,VND40,000 for 2 servings.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.86,0:29:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you know that I'm here?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.96,0:29:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,By watching your live stream.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.11,0:29:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.62,0:29:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I have 2 servings. 
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.43,0:29:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A foreign sponsor donates VND500,000\N to the character of the show today.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.21,0:29:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- Here's your VND500,000. \N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.97,0:30:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,2 servings, please.\N VND500,000 from a foreign sponsor.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.17,0:30:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,VND800,000 for 2 servings.\N VND400,000 for each.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.06,0:30:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a new record, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.14,0:30:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[VND400,000 for a bowl of rice noodle soup]
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.53,0:30:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.83,0:30:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- This is for him. No need to give me the food.\N- Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.43,0:30:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[Have you got surprised?]
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.46,0:30:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,VND200,000 for no food.\N Sounds a bit weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.00,0:30:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.41,0:30:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.44,0:30:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She wanna give a chance to other customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.68,0:30:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very kind of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.62,0:30:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- A serving at VND100,000, please.\N- Thanks a ton.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.48,0:30:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,VND100,000 for this serving.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.12,0:30:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,One serving, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.48,0:30:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm a huge fan of yours, Color Man.\N- Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.12,0:30:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,One more serving.\N Alright, here you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.51,0:30:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- Two servings, please!\N- Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.32,0:30:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just buy one or two servings, everyone.\N Try to make this challenge harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.00,0:30:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The food will be easily sold out\N if you buy a few servings at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.27,0:30:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it harder.\N If you fail it, I'll donate more money to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.29,0:30:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thanks for your support.\N- Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.88,0:30:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, everyone.\N The challenge is to sell 150 servings.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.46,0:30:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you come to support us,\N please don't buy too many servings at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.82,0:31:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one or two servings.\N Make the challenge more difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.56,0:31:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and let more customers support Thanh and Minh Tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.96,0:31:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If I fail to sell 150 bowls\N of rice noodle soup within 90 minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.89,0:31:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to give him VND10 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.05,0:31:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I wanna fail this challenge.\N So just come to buy one or two servings.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.34,0:31:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.18,0:31:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A serving at VND200,000 for this little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.81,0:31:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- Which grade are you in?\N- I'm in the fifth grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.74,0:31:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.05,0:31:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You look more handsome than on the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.07,0:31:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.74,0:31:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- Five servings, please.\N- Give us a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.12,0:31:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- You've just checked out my eatery.\N- Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.76,0:31:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Com Nha 1989 eatery.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.75,0:31:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I remember.\N It's such a great rice eatery.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.79,0:31:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,VND500,000 for 5 servings.\N Thanks very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.19,0:31:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.52,0:31:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- Do you know Com Nha 1989 eatery?\N- Check it out again if you have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.13,0:31:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your support. Bye for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.30,0:31:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,One serving for you.\N Such an adorable kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.95,0:31:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,VND20,000 for one serving.\N Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.37,0:32:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- Two more customers.\N- VND200,000 for 2 servings.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.03,0:32:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And one serving at VND50,000 for this lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.64,0:32:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Three servings in total.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.78,0:32:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Two servings, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.05,0:32:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.48,0:32:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.35,0:32:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,One customer can buy only one serving.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.68,0:32:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't catch up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.65,0:32:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[Working non-stop]
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.90,0:32:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What now? I'm a bit overwhelmed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.17,0:32:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[Lots of customers are waiting]
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.17,0:32:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't catch up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.41,0:32:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you sing or do something to buy the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.24,0:32:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, everyone! One customer can only buy one serving.\N We can't catch up with your orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.28,0:32:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- One serving, please.\N- Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.26,0:32:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd better take some photos to buy the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.11,0:32:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm a big fan of your.\N- Thanks, sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.42,0:32:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No one eats at our place, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.44,0:32:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.60,0:32:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all up to you to decide the price.\N Thanks for your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.85,0:32:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The organizers only allow me to sell one customer a serving.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.57,0:32:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My Goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.88,0:33:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's challenging!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.45,0:33:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They wanna make it harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.84,0:33:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here, sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.48,0:33:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stay here and enjoy rice noodle soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.64,0:33:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,VND100,000 for 5 servings.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.83,0:33:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a minute, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.64,0:33:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,One serving at VND20,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.04,0:33:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- Excuse me?\N- One serving costs VND20,000, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.88,0:33:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just allowed to sell one serving for a customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.35,0:33:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- I wanna buy 2 servings for my children.\N- That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.40,0:33:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- How many servings?\N- Five, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.32,0:33:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Five, right?\N- My great-grandma wanna support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.05,0:33:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.04,0:33:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for a second, sis.\N Her change is VND400,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.31,0:33:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh, why does it take so long?\N Let me give him a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.41,0:33:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[Are you sure?]
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.34,0:33:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,May I enjoy one bowl right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.16,0:33:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one serving for each customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.25,0:33:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't catch up with the orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.72,0:33:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,One customer one serving!\N The challenge is harder for me to overcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.06,0:33:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.02,0:33:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,One serving at VND100,000.\N Thanks very much, sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.39,0:34:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, beloved viewers.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.83,0:34:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't expect things would go like this.\N Now just play it by ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.06,0:34:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Our crew visited Quang Trung Museum this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.82,0:34:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to Dai Kinh Thien in Tay Son,\N where the locals annually make the offerings to King Quang Trung.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.70,0:34:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It might bring us lots of good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.18,0:34:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So many customers come here to support us.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.48,0:34:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hello, uncle.\N- Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.84,0:34:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I have 2 servings.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.22,0:34:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- Would you mind getting just one?\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.28,0:34:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.87,0:34:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- Two servings, please.\N- One for me, the other for my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.76,0:34:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.97,0:34:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- One for your mom. \N- Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.53,0:34:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Two servings.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.61,0:34:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,One customer, one serving.\N How about two?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.17,0:34:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[What do you mean?]
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.10,0:34:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- Alright.\N- Give me some slices of lime, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.63,0:34:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.11,0:34:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- I have one bowl, please.\N- That's nice! Just one customer, one serving.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.64,0:35:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Make the challenge harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.89,0:35:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Your food has been sold out, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.46,0:35:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How many servings are left?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.63,0:35:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How many bowls?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.03,0:35:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- How many?\N- 30 bowls, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.33,0:35:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- More than 30 servings.\N- Around 40.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.44,0:35:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.27,0:35:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[Hang in there, Thanh]
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.52,0:35:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You've just sold 73 servings, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.84,0:35:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen,\N we've just finished 73 servings.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.88,0:35:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[73 servings in 45 minutes]
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.18,0:35:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,77 servings to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.15,0:35:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just 5:50 pm now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.36,0:35:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hope that I can accomplish the challenge in 60 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.41,0:35:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give us some minutes, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.88,0:35:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- I have one serving.\N- Okay, good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.76,0:35:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.46,0:35:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,One for this man, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.26,0:35:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- Keep the change for the owners.\N- Oh, thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.38,0:35:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,One serving at VND40,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.93,0:35:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,One more, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.73,0:35:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.32,0:35:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,VND150,000 for 6 servings, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.96,0:35:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just 2 servings per customer are the maximum.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.08,0:35:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, 2 servings.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.40,0:35:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She wanna buy 6 servings but couldn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.09,0:36:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[The number of the servings: 97]
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.22,0:36:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please try to understand.\N Thank you a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.15,0:36:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- How about you?\N- 2 servings, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.89,0:36:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Two servings, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.04,0:36:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, everyone! His rice noodle soup doesn't have a fixed price today.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.00,0:36:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have two, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.96,0:36:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How adorable! VND100,000 for 2 servings.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.48,0:36:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a ton.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.49,0:36:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,One more, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.76,0:36:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The prices of almost all the servings are doubled.\N Thanks, sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.85,0:36:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.10,0:36:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My husband is holding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.04,0:36:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, her husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.72,0:36:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,One customer buys one serving.\N So that more people can come here to support us.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.67,0:36:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.04,0:36:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,One serving for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.73,0:36:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why a lot, sis? Please go out this way.\N Thanks a ton.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.16,0:36:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,VND50,000 for this serving.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.56,0:36:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your support, everyone.\N Just one serving per customer is maximum.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.60,0:36:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[What are you looking for?]
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.21,0:36:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- Out of rice noodles, huh?\N- There's still some left.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.32,0:36:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[We're preparing it]
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.14,0:37:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- I just give him VND100,000. No food is needed.\N- Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.01,0:37:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She donated VND100,000 to the owners.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.69,0:37:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen, we've already sold 110 servings.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.95,0:37:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Forty servings left to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.52,0:37:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,One customer, one serving!\N 40 servings left!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.46,0:37:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- Come here, please.\N- May I take a photo with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.52,0:37:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the money. No food is needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.54,0:37:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, they even don't want the food.\N Thanks a ton.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.77,0:37:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad that we can save more food.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.22,0:37:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- How much broth do we have left?\N- A lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.15,0:37:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[Don't worry]
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.01,0:37:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a pot of broth?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.12,0:37:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- Or just boiling water?\N- It's for parboiling the rice noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.69,0:37:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We've still got much broth\N but gonna run out of other ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.04,0:37:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.01,0:37:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The ingredients are just enough for 150 bowls.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.64,0:37:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the fastest he could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.22,0:37:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Two bowls, please.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.08,0:37:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,One customer, one serving, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.02,0:37:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,One, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.90,0:37:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one serving for each customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.74,0:37:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna sit here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.26,0:37:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Two servings for us, please.\N We'd like to enjoy the food here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.41,0:37:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.61,0:37:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sit here, right?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.92,0:38:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Two bowls of rice noodle soup, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.77,0:38:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,One more serving, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.55,0:38:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Only one bowl per customer.\N We're gonna sell out the rice noodle soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.90,0:38:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'd like one serving, please.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.71,0:38:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How about 2 assorted servings?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.82,0:38:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,One customer can buy one serving.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.31,0:38:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost out of the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.50,0:38:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Please try to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.94,0:38:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You can come here tomorrow.\N Thanks, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.39,0:38:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to donate this amount of money to the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.76,0:38:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He buys a serving at VND1 million! Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.61,0:38:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wish you health and happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.31,0:38:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh, we've just broken a new record.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.28,0:38:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A serving at VND1 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.23,0:38:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hata Hotel in Quy Nhon donates VND1 million to the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.97,0:38:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it, uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.51,0:38:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,An old man from the Hata hotel in Quy Nhon\N bought a bowl at VN1 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.16,0:38:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got 2 servings at VND1 million/each.\N Thanks for your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.08,0:38:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.05,0:39:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, girl. Go out this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.97,0:39:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad! I almost forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.12,0:39:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit overwhelmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.83,0:39:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- I wanna send him some money.\N- Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.57,0:39:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She's donating money to him.\N No food needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.72,0:39:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,One customer, one serving, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.79,0:39:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The elderly should be given priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.45,0:39:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Each customer can buy only one serving.\N We're almost out of the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.93,0:39:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,One bowl, right?\N Move here, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.70,0:39:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- And one for you, huh?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.14,0:39:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,One bowl of you two, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.39,0:39:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.68,0:39:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.41,0:39:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, lords!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.52,0:39:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your savings, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.85,0:39:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[You know it all]
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.68,0:39:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,One customer, one serving, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.62,0:39:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.11,0:39:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna run out of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.36,0:39:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you buy just one bowl?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.70,0:39:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[I agree]
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.56,0:39:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All for one serving, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.28,0:40:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We've just got more than 10 servings left.\N Please try to understand, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.57,0:40:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, little girl.\N Move here to take a photo with me, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.16,0:40:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got only 5 bowls left.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.09,0:40:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, everyone.\N There are only 5 servings left.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.26,0:40:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please try to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.00,0:40:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,One serving.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.23,0:40:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.17,0:40:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Three servings left.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.49,0:40:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The last 3 bowls.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.80,0:40:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,One for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.60,0:40:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You can come here to take a photo with me, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.74,0:40:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for supporting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.73,0:40:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Two more left.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.66,0:40:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,One for you, right? Alright, thanks a bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.94,0:40:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the last serving.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.84,0:40:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A sponsor from Switzerland\N wanna send this to the owners.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.42,0:40:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.96,0:40:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,One serving at VND50,000 for this woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.91,0:40:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A sponsor from Switzerland sent us VND1 million.
